title: #43: Software Millionare (David Taylor)
itunes:title: Software Millionare with David Taylor
description: David Taylor stopped by Skeptic Tank Studios (my apartment) to talk about his days as a working professional in the software industry during the tech boom. He gave it all up to become a struggling comedian and talented non-working writer.
